\c 112 
\m \bd Faarfannaa \bd*\bd 112\bd*
\s2 \bdit \zbr\bdit*Eebba Sodaa Waaqayyoo Keessaa Argamu
\m \bd 1\bd* Waaqayyoon jajadhaa! Namni Waaqayyoon sodaatu, inni abboommiin isaa guddaa itti tolus haa gammadu.
\m \bd 2\bd* Sanyiin isaa biyyicha keessatti guddaa in ta'a, dhaloonni warra gara-qajeelotaa in eebbifama.
\m \bd 3\bd* Badhaadhummaa fi soorumni mana isaa keessa jira, qajeelummaan isaas yeroo hundumaaf jabaatee in dhaabata.
\m \bd 4\bd* Inni araara-qabeessa, oo'a-qabeessa, qajeelaas waan ta'eef, warra gara-qajeelotaaf ifni dukkana keessatti in ba'aaf.
\m \bd 5\bd* Namni araara argisiisuu fi namni liqeessu gaarii dha, inni jiruu isaa qajeeltootti in geggeeffata!
\m \bd 6\bd* Inni yoom iyyuu hin mittiqu, namni qajeelaanoo bara baraan in yaadatama.
\m \bd 7\bd* Oduu hamaa dhaga'uu hin sodaatu, Waaqayyoon waan amanatuuf garaan isaa hin shakku.
\m \bd 8\bd* Hamma warra isa cunqursan irratti wanta dhufu argee gammadutti, garaan isaa cimsee amanateera, hin sodaatu.
\m \bd 9\bd* Inni arjummaadhaan warra dhabaniif in kenna, qajeelummaan isaa yeroo hundumaaf jabaatee in dhaabata; gaanfi mataa isaa ulfinaan ol in qabama.
\m \bd 10\bd* Namni jal'aan kana argee in aara, ilkaan isaa walitti in qara, ofii isaatiis gad in dhuma; fedhi warra jal'ootaa waan tokkotti kan hin galle in ta'a.
\b 
